        "username": "rread",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2011-03-22 15:44:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\nlet's fix rhel6 later and document the requirement.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
